images

类 TaggableImage

  • java.lang.Object
    • images.TaggableImage

  • public class TaggableImage
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing an image and an associated tag of the type ImageTag. Images can be tagged as UNTAGGED, NONINFRINGEMENT or INFRINGMENT.
    作者:
    James McCann (mccannjame), 300192420
